extends ../layout

block content

  div(class="mb-6")
    h1(class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 tracking-tight" style="margin-bottom:2px") Connect an agent
    p(class="text-sm text-gray-500") Give your agent a name — get a file to drop in its project folder.

  if !token
    //- ── Step 1: form ──
    div(class="card max-w-lg")
      div(class="card-header"): span(class="card-title") Agent details
      div(class="card-body")
        form(method="POST" action="/connect" class="flex flex-col gap-4")
          div
            label(class="label") Agent name
            input(class="field" type="text" name="name" placeholder="e.g. Hermes, BiotechRoles CEO, My Scraper" required autofocus)
          div
            label(class="label") Role
            input(class="field" type="text" name="role" placeholder="e.g. Outreach, Engineering, Research")
          div
            label(class="label") AI model
            select(class="field" name="model")
              optgroup(label="Claude (auto-sync via file watcher)")
                option(value="claude-sonnet-4-6") Claude Sonnet 4.6
                option(value="claude-opus-4-6") Claude Opus 4.6
                option(value="claude-haiku-4-5") Claude Haiku 4.5
              optgroup(label="Other (reports via API)")
                option(value="gpt-4o") GPT-4o
                option(value="gpt-4o-mini") GPT-4o mini
                option(value="gemini-1.5-pro") Gemini 1.5 Pro
                option(value="mistral-large") Mistral Large
                option(value="other") Other / Unknown
          div
            label(class="label") Color
            select(class="field" name="color")
              each c in ['teal','amber','purple','green','gray']
                option(value=c)= c.charAt(0).toUpperCase()+c.slice(1)
          if error
            p(class="text-sm text-red-500")= error
          button(class="btn btn-teal" type="submit") Generate connection file →

  else
    //- ── Step 2: success + instructions ──
    div(class="grid gap-5 max-w-2xl")

      div(class="card border-2" style="border-color:#14b8a6")
        div(class="card-body flex items-center gap-4")
          div(class=`w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-base font-bold av-${agent.color}`)= agent.initials
          div
            div(class="font-bold text-gray-900")= agent.name
            div(class="text-sm text-gray-500")= agent.role
          div(class="ml-auto")
            span(class="pill pill-idle")
              span(class="sdot")
              |  connected

      //- ── Claude Code path ──
      if isClaudeCode
        div(class="card")
          div(class="card-header"): span(class="card-title") How to connect (Claude Code)
          div(class="card-body flex flex-col gap-5")

            div
              p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-1") 1. Download the connection file
              p(class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-3") This file tells your agent how to report its work to the dashboard.
              a(class="btn btn-teal inline-flex items-center gap-2" href=`/connect/claude-md?name=${encodeURIComponent(agent.name)}&token=${token}` download="CLAUDE.md")
                | ↓ Download CLAUDE.md

            div
              p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-1") 2. Drop it in the agent's project folder
              div(class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border border-gray-100 px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs text-gray-700")
                | your-project/
                br
                | ├── CLAUDE.md   ← drop it here
                br
                | ├── src/
                br
                | └── ...

            div
              p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-1") 3. Start your agent
              p(class="text-xs text-gray-500") The agent reads CLAUDE.md automatically and will start reporting its actions to this dashboard as it works. The file watcher will also pick up Claude Code sessions from this project automatically.

      //- ── Non-Claude path ──
      else
        div(class="card")
          div(class="card-header"): span(class="card-title") How to connect (any AI model)
          div(class="card-body flex flex-col gap-5")

            div
              p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-1") Option A — paste a system prompt
              p(class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-3") Download and paste this into your agent's system prompt (works with GPT, Gemini, Mistral, etc.).
              a(class="btn btn-teal inline-flex items-center gap-2" href=`/connect/system-prompt?name=${encodeURIComponent(agent.name)}&token=${token}` download="erpofone-system-prompt.txt")
                | ↓ Download system prompt

            div
              p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-1") Option B — agent self-registers
              p(class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-2") Tell your agent to call this endpoint once at the start of a session — it will get back its token and reporting instructions automatically.
              div(class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border border-gray-100 px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs text-gray-700 break-all whitespace-pre-wrap")
                | curl -s -X POST #{hqUrl}/api/ingest/register \
                br
                |   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
                br
                |   -d '{"name":"#{agent.name}","role":"#{agent.role}","model":"#{model}"}'

            div
              p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-1") What you get back
              div(class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border border-gray-100 px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs text-gray-700")
                | { "token": "...", "agentName": "#{agent.name}", "quickstart": "..." }
              p(class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2") The agent reads the quickstart field and knows exactly how to report. No other setup needed.

      div(class="card")
        div(class="card-header"): span(class="card-title") Your ingest token
        div(class="card-body")
          p(class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-2") Keep this private. It's already embedded in the files above.
          div(class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border border-gray-100 px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs text-gray-700 break-all")= token

      div(class="flex gap-3")
        a(class="btn btn-gray" href="/connect") ← Connect another agent
        a(class="btn btn-gray" href="/agents") View all agents →
